data.description: What a cutie! This property delights with updated kitchen and baths boasting new solid wood construction cabinetry, granite countertops, tile, and bamboo flooring.  Enjoy the fine Florida weather in the large multi-purpose Florida room. This property also features a newer roof (2007) and a newer A/C (2014) and newer hot water heater (2011) The house is wheel chair accessible featuring ramp to front door and into kitchen from garage and wide master door and front bathroom door. Spacious two car garage allows two cars or tons of extra storage space! Complete irrigation system on well allows for beautiful grass all year long!
